{"tid":2449342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【求推】革命不是餵飯，希望呢個post係最後一啖","createTime":"2021-03-16T14:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T04:02:33.000Z","uid":271092,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"057df4d06f1ce345d9ceafeedad9534ac55182ec","tid":2449342,"uid":271092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c7Sjf9t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc7Sjf9t.png&h=2d7a26d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">相信大家都見過一個page<br />\n咁最近一個page發生咩事呢<br />\n呢度講一講，反思一下自己點接收資訊 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實呢一個page已經有好多文宣page/KOL不滿，最主要原因都係cap圖唔tag原作。佢呢一個account原本係個人account，叫kenny，Google search &quot;Kennyeatplaysleep&quot; 你就會連佢嘅微博都見到，渣打銀行銷售主任吖嘛。（文匯報齊正之快啲寫呢一篇文，萬分感激） <br />\n<br />\n多謝連登巴打出手，喺3月16日，佢deactive咗個account。 <br />\n<br />\n呢啲事跡的唔多講，連登有好多人講緊。<br />\n我並唔反對有人好有心咁樣做資訊整合，但最少都要畀返個credit（因為我都畀佢cap過圖， 從眾多文宣page都係，因為對佢有不滿，所以佢ban咗我）。 <br />\n<br />\n問題係，佢玩膠。有成十幾萬人，睇佢啲膠post。 <br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以支持一下其他有用嘅page，立場蘋果之外，仲有好多選擇，自由港post已經有好多好page推介。 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">大家應該要 接收更加多嘅資訊， 增進自己嘅知識，革命唔係餵飯</span><br />\n<br />\n要大家download支那寶用嗰五千蚊嘅事後家明&hellip;&hellip;遲啲再講啦。 <br />\n<br />\n//小弟野子，閒時寫文，感情民生經濟政治想講就講，環保撚，養生健身，普法教育<br />\n放個payme link 隨便請我飲茶🙏<br />\n鳩噏文歡迎分享。 <br />\n<br />\nMewe 野子<br />\nYouTube 野子syz<br />\nIg/tg @clisyz //<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMe6WDFFngC/?igshid=1d5xqhw6hhsaz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMe6WDFFngC%2F%3Figshid%3D1d5xqhw6hhsaz&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=07e61015\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMe6WDFFngC%2F%3Figshid%3D1d5xqhw6hhsaz&h=08113720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CMe6WDFFngC/?igshid=1d5xqhw6hhsaz</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">呢個post我會貼啲高質page比大家<br />\n有講歷史，講本土論述，講政治等等</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c6ff5acef9eda8d4fe172431a831ed03b8947a","tid":2449342,"uid":271092,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">有心人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/caringperson.channel?igshid=1njynb5zdg8vm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fcaringperson.channel%3Figshid%3D1njynb5zdg8vm&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=40c60020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/caringperson.channel?igshid=1njynb5zdg8vm</a><br />\n<br />\n呢一個係我最欣賞嘅page之一，好正，有深度有見解，經濟政治社會都會講。<br />\n對人最nice嘅文宣page<br />\n<br />\n版主比劉x良個城寨屌做五毛，仲要block埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d260ef77c61b0b2c2571f67bbdcf425f7aea09ed","tid":2449342,"uid":271092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:21:23.000Z","msg":"自由港 Harbour of freedom<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/harbouroffreedom?igshid=f0r5y4e2e4mq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fharbouroffreedom%3Figshid%3Df0r5y4e2e4mq&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=9a53c149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/harbouroffreedom?igshid=f0r5y4e2e4mq</a><br />\n<br />\n《自由港》是一本由一群海外港人創立的政治刊物。主要刊登各方面不同的論述及評論，以及不同海外抗爭者的專訪。<br />\n<br />\n雖然身處海外，但我們希望能略盡棉力，建立一個能夠暢所欲言，能夠自由講的避風塘。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n聯絡我們：<br />\nEmail: HarbourofFreedom@ProtonMail.com<br />\nFacebook: @HarbourofFreedomHongKong<br />\nIG:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/harbouroffreedom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.